  <brief_title>Exploring Vancomycin Disposition in Neonates</brief_title>
  <official_title>Exploring Vancomycin Disposition in Neonates: Paired Analysis of Vancomycin Concentrations Using Immunoassay and Liquid-chromatography-tandem Mass Spectrometry. Determination of Vancomycin Protein Binding and Its Covariates in Neonates</official_title>
